binarization.cpp :--

to compile type below line in the terminal

g++ -ggdb `pkg-config --cflags opencv` -o `basename binarization.cpp .cpp` binarization.cpp `pkg-config --libs opencv`


to run

./binarization 1.jpg#path of the image file needed as a argument(image must be grayscale-1 channel)

Stroke of the width:10(my choice)



